nsider.com%20(Jordan%20Hart)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnike-salaries-how-much-employees-paid-software-engineer-design-tech-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22All%20publicity%20is%20good%20publicity%3A%20How%20Astronomer's%20viral%20moment%20could%20be%20a%20'blessing%20in%20disguise'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22811%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Coldplay's%20Chris%20Martin.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687bb61df748d8c055f5ecd9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22608%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EColdplay's%20Chris%20Martin.%3Cp%3ERobert%20Okine%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20'kiss%20cam'%20video%20appeared%20to%20show%20Astronomer's%20CEO%20embracing%20the%20firm's%20head%20of%20HR.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20incident%20went%20viral%20around%20the%20world%20and%20led%20to%20CEO%20Andy%20Byron%20resigning.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20not%20the%20kind%20of%20publicity%20Astronomer%20would%20likely%20have%20hoped%20for%2C%20but%20it%20could%20benefit%20the%20firm.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20eyes%20this%20week%20have%20been%20on%20a%20once-little-known%20tech%20company%20called%20Astronomer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20not%20been%20the%20kind%20of%20attention%20Astronomer%20would%20likely%20have%20hoped%20for%2C%20it's%20been%20said%20that%20all%20publicity%20is%20good%20publicity%2C%20and%20some%20public%20relations%20experts%20who%20spoke%20to%20Business%20Insider%20said%20the%20newfound%20fame%20could%2C%20ultimately%2C%20benefit%20the%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20viral%20moment%20that%20catapulted%20the%20data%20company%20into%20the%20global%20spotlight%20took%20place%20at%20a%20Coldplay%20concert%20near%20Boston%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20when%20a%20%26quot%3Bkiss%20cam%26quot%3B%20appeared%20to%20show%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fastronomer-ceo-andy-byron-resigns-viral-kiss-cam-incident-coldplay-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethen-Astronomer%20CEO%20Andy%20Byron%3C%2Fa%3E%20embracing%20the%20company's%20head%20of%20human%20resources%2C%20Kristin%20Cabot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20spotting%20themselves%20on%20the%20big%20screen%2C%20the%20clearly%20panicked%20pair%20attempted%20to%20dodge%20the%20camera%2C%20prompting%20Coldplay%20front%20man%20Chris%20Martin%20to%20speculate%20that%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Bhaving%20an%20affair%20or%20they're%20just%20very%20shy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20clip%20shot%20around%20the%20world%20and%20fueled%20a%20torrent%20of%20memes%20and%20internet%20sleuthing.%20Even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoldplay-kiss-cam-memes-tesla-netflix-stubhub-mariners-brands-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emajor%20brands%20like%20Netflix%3C%2Fa%3E%20got%20in%20on%20the%20viral%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERyan%20McCormick%2C%20cofounder%20of%20Goldman%20McCormick%2C%20a%20public%20relations%20firm%20in%20New%20York%2C%20described%20it%20as%20a%20possible%20%26quot%3Bblessing%20in%20disguise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20real%20silver%20lining%20is%20that%20if%20this%20company%20is%20doing%20something%20truly%20innovative%20and%20they're%20doing%20something%20truly%20groundbreaking%2C%20the%20likelihood%20of%20someone%20finding%20them%20has%20increased%20substantially%2C%26quot%3B%20McCormick%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20short%20term%2C%20they're%20embedded%20in%20controversy%2C%20but%20they're%20going%20to%20have%20people%20looking%20at%20them%20in%20a%20way%20they've%20never%20done%20before.%20I%20think%20that%20they'll%20probably%20come%20out%20OK.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20on%20Friday%2C%20Astronomer%20said%20its%20leaders%20were%20%26quot%3Bexpected%20to%20set%20the%20standard%20in%20both%20conduct%20and%20accountability%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20it%20had%20launched%20a%20%26quot%3Bformal%20investigation%26quot%3B%20into%20the%20incident.%20It%20added%20that%20Byron%20had%20been%20placed%20on%20leave.%20On%20Saturday%2C%20it%20said%20the%20exec%20had%20resigned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcCormick%20said%20Byron's%20departure%20would%20create%20some%20distance%20between%20the%20viral%20drama%20and%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20they%20took%20the%20high%20road.%20They%20did%20what%20needed%20to%20be%20done%2C%20which%20was%20probably%20a%20hard%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20McCormick%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20were%20an%20investor%20or%20employee%20at%20that%20company%2C%20I%20would%20feel%20pretty%20confident.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20used%20its%20Saturday%20statement%20to%20draw%20attention%20to%20its%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20this%20week%2C%20we%20were%20known%20as%20a%20pioneer%20in%20the%20DataOps%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20awareness%20of%20our%20company%20may%20have%20changed%20overnight%2C%20our%20product%20and%20our%20work%20for%20our%20customers%20have%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMike%20Fahey%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Fahey%20Communications%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20this%20showed%20the%20company%20was%20making%20%26quot%3Ba%20concerted%20effort%20to%20redirect%20the%20narrative%20to%20where%20it%20is%20favorable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAstronomer%20is%20fighting%20back%2C%20working%20to%20position%20its%20offerings%20and%20overall%20customer%20experience%20as%20strong%20and%20reliable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20company%20%26quot%3Bnow%20has%20more%20eyes%20on%20it%20than%20ever%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20New%20York-based%20firm%20had%20initially%20remained%20silent%20as%20the%20social%20media%20storm%20gathered%20force%20and%20users%20flooded%20its%20channels%20with%20comments%2C%20which%20Fahey%20said%20was%20a%20mistake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20timing%20of%20the%20statement%20was%20notably%20delayed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20Astronomer's%20Friday%20announcement.%20%26quot%3BThe%20absence%20of%20official%20communication%20created%20a%20void%20quickly%20filled%20by%20rumors%2C%20fake%20statements%2C%20and%20memes%20that%20spread%20widely%20on%20social%20media.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20viral%20post%20included%20a%20fake%20apology%20letter%20attributed%20to%20Byron%20that%20featured%20a%20lyric%20from%20a%20Coldplay%20song.%20It%20was%20widely%20assumed%20to%20be%20real%20and%20picked%20apart%20relentlessly%20online.%20Astronomer%20said%20Friday%20that%20Byron%20had%20not%20made%20any%20statement%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Breports%20saying%20otherwise%20are%20all%20incorrect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKristi%20Piehl%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Media%20Minefield%2C%20said%20the%20company%20made%20the%20same%20mistake%20as%20the%20pair%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bkiss%20cam.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20that%20they%20reacted%20online%20and%20on%20social%20media%20is%20exactly%20how%20the%20two%20people%20involved%20reacted.%20When%20the%20camera%20hit%20them%2C%20they%20hid%2C%26quot%3B%20Piehl%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20impression%20is%20so%20important.%20And%20the%20company%20allowed%20the%20first%20impression%20to%20be%20social%20media%2C%20the%20internet%2C%20and%20strangers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeirdre%20Latour%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Rebellis%20Communications%2C%20also%20suggested%20the%20company%20had%20gotten%20it%20wrong%20with%20its%20initial%20silence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20just%20the%20worst%20version%20of%20PR%20malpractice%20that%20you%20can%20see%20from%20a%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20letting%20this%20terribly%20worded%20statement%2C%20blaming%20Coldplay%20and%20others%2C%20fester%20out%20in%20the%20marketplace.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20the%20situation%20was%