ge%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20their%20earnings%20go%20up%20without%20having%20to%20work%20more%20hours.%20%26quot%3BNow%20they're%20serving%2010%20people%20at%20once%20and%20therefore%20making%20about%2010%20times%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20level%2C%20%26quot%3Bone-to-infinity%20leverage%2C%26quot%3B%20can%20create%20life-changing%20wealth.%20This%20is%20when%20the%20trainer%20builds%20an%20app%20with%20weekly%20workouts%20and%20a%20meal%20plan%20feature%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20could%20create%20that%20app%20once%2C%20and%20millions%20of%20people%20around%20the%20world%20can%20subscribe%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Han.%20%26quot%3BThat%20concept%20really%20was%20the%20key%20that%20I%20unlocked.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22rose%20han%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687a861685e81483682e49f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHan%20resides%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Rose%20Han%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20didn't%20get%20to%20one-to-infinity%20leverage%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20business%20began%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20a%20coworking%20space%2C%20where%20she%20hosted%20free%20personal%20finance%20classes%20based%20on%20her%20own%20experience%20paying%20down%20debt%20and%20using%20index%20funds%20to%20grow%20her%20net%20worth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20just%20learning%20a%20lot%20on%20my%20financial%20awakening%20journey%2C%20so%20I%20wanted%20to%20share%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20back%20of%20my%20mind%2C%20I%20thought%2C%20'OK%2C%20maybe%20there's%20some%20way%20I%20could%20make%20this%20lucrative%2C'%20but%20that's%20not%20the%20goal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20hosted%20free%20classes%20for%20nearly%20two%20years%2C%20until%20she%20gained%20the%20confidence%20to%20start%20charging.%20Then%2C%20instead%20of%20keeping%20the%20class%20within%20the%20coworking%20space%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20YouTube%2C%20where%20her%20reach%20would%20be%20far%20greater.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20that%20a%20video%20could%20reach%20millions%20of%20people%2C%2024%2F7%2C%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life%20and%20even%20after%2C%20that%20was%20really%20just%20wild%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Han.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20skeptical%20because%20I'd%20never%20gone%20on%20camera.%20It%20was%20scary.%20But%2C%20after%20about%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20of%20doing%20these%20free%20meetups%2C%20I%20got%20the%20courage%20to%20press%20record%20and%20post%20my%20first%20video.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40itsrosehan%2Fvideos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20nearly%20one%20million%20subscribers%2C%20has%20evolved%20into%20a%20financial%20education%20company%20that%20earns%20money%20through%20online%20courses%2C%20brand%20deals%2C%20affiliate%20links%2C%20and%20book%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20launched%20her%20first%20online%20course%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20brought%20in%20%24160%2C000%20%26quot%3Bin%20a%20matter%20of%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20made%20in%20seven%20days%20what%20used%20to%20take%20me%20an%20entire%20year%20to%20make.%20Granted%2C%20I%20worked%20a%20lot%20to%20create%20that%20course%2C%20and%20it%20didn't%20just%20happen%20in%20seven%20days%2C%20but%20I%20created%20something%20once%20that%20I%20could%20sell%20over%20and%20over%20and%20over%20and%20serve%20a%20lot%20of%20people.%20I%20created%20a%20lot%20of%20value%20with%20something%2C%20and%20so%20I%20got%20paid%20in%20that%20exponential%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d214e4cb-f1a8-45d9-b7f6-53112dabafb1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20apply%20the%20one-to-infinity%20mindset%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20use%20the%20one-to-infinity%20model%20and%20earn%20exponentially%2C%20start%20by%20asking%3A%20What%20value%20can%20I%20provide%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20fully%20believe%20that%20the%20more%20value%20you%20provide%2C%20the%20more%20you%20can%20earn%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Han.%20%26quot%3BAnd%2C%20if%20you%20think%20creatively%20enough%2C%20there's%20no%20limit%20to%20how%20much%20value%20you%20can%20provide%20and%20therefore%20how%20much%20money%20you%20can%20earn.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20holdup%20for%20her%20was%20confidence%2C%20and%20convincing%20herself%20that%20she%20was%20providing%20something%20valuable%20enough%20to%20get%20paid%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20this%20is%20the%20challenge%20for%20most%20people.%20They%20think%2C%20'Oh%2C%20I%20should%20make%20more%20money.%20I%20need%20to%20ask%20for%20a%20raise%20and%20get%20a%20higher-paying%20career.'%20But%20their%20first%20obstacle%20is%20thinking%2C%20'Who%20am%20I%20to%20do%20that%3F%20I%20don't%20have%20the%20skills.%20I%20don't%20have%20anything%20of%20value%20to%20provide.'%20That%20sort%20of%20mindset%20of%2C%20'I'm%20not%20capable.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHan%20overcame%20that%20mindset%20by%20taking%20action%20%E2%80%94%20by%20hosting%20the%20free%20meet-ups%20and%20getting%20real-world%20feedback%20that%20her%20money%20lessons%20were%20helping%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKnow%20that%20you%20have%20the%20ability%20within%20you%20to%20create%20a%20lot%20of%20value%20for%20the%20world%20and%20therefore%20generate%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20that's%20like%20within%20your%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20just%20have%20to%20find%20the%20confidence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fself-made-millionaire-shares-the-key-to-earning-leveraged-income-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753004702000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%