's%20fashion%20boutique%20is%20on%20a%20growth%20spurt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20of%20the%20new%20Aritzia%20flagship%20store%20at%20555%20N.%20Michigan%20Ave.%20in%20Chicago.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6853236ef748d8c055f3ffb0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAritzia%20has%20been%20having%20a%20good%20year.%20%3Cp%3ETerrence%20Antonio%20James%2FChicago%20Tribune%2FTribune%20News%20Service%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAritzia%20CEO%20Jennifer%20Wong%20laid%20out%20some%20ambitious%20goals%20last%20year%20for%20a%20US%20expansion.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%2C%20the%20women's%20wear%20retailer%20appears%20to%20be%20beating%20expectations%20for%20store%20count%20and%20sales.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBI%20took%20a%20closer%20look%20at%20the%2041-year-old%20company%20that%20is%20seeing%20a%20new%20chapter%20of%20success.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWatch%20out%2C%20Lululemon%3A%20Another%20Vancouver-based%20apparel%20maker%20is%20making%20a%20play%20for%20US%20shoppers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAritzia%2C%20the%20everyday%20luxury%20womenswear%20retailer%2C%20has%20steadily%20gained%20ground%20and%20grown%20sales%20over%20the%20past%20several%20years%20with%20its%20assortment%20of%20stylish%20activewear%20and%20comfortable%20office%20wear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20in%20July%20that%20it%20grew%20its%20retail%20footprint%20by%2025%25%20over%20the%20last%20year%2C%20including%20opening%2013%20stores%20and%20redesigning%20three%20existing%20ones.%20The%20expansion%20helped%20drive%20retail%20sales%20up%2034%25%20year%20over%20year%20last%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20done%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20over%20the%20past%201%201%2F2%20years%2C%20two%20years%20to%20refine%20our%20playbook%20and%20ensure%20that%20our%20inventory%20is%20productive%20and%20efficient.%20And%20I%20think%20we're%20in%20a%20fantastic%20place%20right%20now%2C%20very%20well-positioned%2C%26quot%3B%20CEO%20Jennifer%20Wong%20said%20in%20an%20earnings%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20appear%20to%20be%20delivering%20on%20some%20ambitious%20goals%20Wong%20laid%20out%20last%20year%20as%20Aritzia's%20US%20expansion%20was%20heating%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWong%20was%20not%20immediately%20available%20for%20an%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider%2C%20but%20she%20detailed%20her%20strategy%20in%20several%20interviews%20with%20other%20outlets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20tackling%20all%20the%20major%20cities%20where%20we%20know%20our%20brand%20and%20product%20resonates%20with%20the%20customer%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voguebusiness.com%2Fstory%2Fconsumers%2Four-goal-is-to-get-famous-in-the-us-how-aritzia-ceo-jennifer-wong-plans-to-conquer-the-states%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20Vogue%20Business%20last%20November.%20%26quot%3BThe%20next%20step%20is%20to%20fill%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%201984%20in%20Vancouver%2C%20Aritzia%20saw%20steady%20growth%20in%20Canada%20before%20entering%20the%20US%20in%202007.%20The%20company%20saw%20a%20bumper%20year%20in%202020%2C%20followed%20by%20some%20pandemic-era%20challenges%2C%20and%20has%20since%20tripled%20sales%20to%20more%20than%20CAD%242.7%20billion%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWong%20has%20been%20with%20the%20company%20since%20its%20early%20days%2C%20rising%20through%20the%20ranks%20to%20eventually%20take%20over%20the%20helm%20from%20founder%20Brian%20Hill%20in%202022.%20She%20soon%20doubled%20the%20rate%20of%20store%20openings%2C%20helping%20to%20extend%20the%20momentum%20of%20the%20return-to-office%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20experienced%20some%20explosive%20growth%20coming%20out%20of%20Covid%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20pent-up%20demand%20and%20a%20whole%20new%20energy.%20That%20really%20accelerated%20our%20business%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20we%20became%20more%20well%20known%20than%20ever.%20We've%20been%20really%20riding%20that%20momentum%20since.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2068%20locations%20in%20Canada%20and%2063%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20the%20company%20says%20it%20could%20see%20the%20US%20figure%20grow%20to%20more%20than%20150%20over%20the%20next%20few%20years%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20its%20growing%20e-commerce%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20of%20those%20locations%20will%20open%20in%20the%20next%20few%20months%20in%20the%20Boston%20area%2C%20Miami%2C%20Salt%20Lake%20City%2C%20and%20Raleigh%2C%20North%20Carolina.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Aritzia's%20stores%20have%20drawn%20some%20derision%20on%20TikTok%20for%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faritzias-mirror-less-dressing-rooms-generating-buzz-social-media-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emirrorless%20(and%20sometimes%20crowded)%20dressing%20rooms%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20its%20high-touch%20%26quot%3Bstyle%20advisor%26quot%3B%20sales%20approach%20harkens%20back%20to%20the%20kind%20of%20personalized%20shopping%20experience%20offered%20at%20luxury%20department%20stores%20like%20Bergdorf%20Goodman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20it's%20the%20clothing%20that%20ultimately%20makes%20or%20breaks%20the%20sale%20for%20fashion%20brands%2C%20and%20Aritzia%20appears%20to%20be%20delivering%20good%20value%20for%20its%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20style%20and%20substance%2C%20BI's%20reviews%20team%20called%20Aritzia's%20apparel%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fdeals%2Faritzia-summer-sale-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20timeless%20and%20elegant%20as%20it%20is%20trendy%20and%20modern%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20the%20quality%20is%20%26quot%3Bundisputed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrice-wise%2C%20analysts%20at%20Jefferies%20looked%20at%20comparable%20products%20from%20nine%20peer%20retailers%20and%20found%20Aritzia%20to%20be%20a%20cut%20above%20the%20mid-tier%20but%20a%20step%20below%20the%20highest-priced%20brands.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20it%20is%20more%20expensive%20than%20Lululemon%20and%20J.%20Crew%20but%20less%20pricey%20than%20Anthropologie%20and%20Madewell.%20In%20addition%2C%20Aritiza's%20prices%20are%20less%20frequently%20marked%20down%20than%20some%20competitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Jefferies%20analysts%20suggested%20that%20the%20relative%20pricing%20and%20demand%20for%20Aritzia%20products%20give%20the%20company%20more%20room%20to%20grow%20in%20sales%20and%20profits%2C%20propelling%20its%20expansion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20its%20merchandise%20to%20stores%20to%20tech%2C%20it%20appears%20Aritzia%20is%20getting%20a%20lot%20of%20retail%20fundamentals%20right%20%E2%80%94%20and%20reaping%20the%20rewards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20any%20one%20of%20those%20things%2C%20but%20it's%20all%20of%20these%20things%20that%20come%20together%20and%20how%20we've%20been%20able%20to%20execute%20well%20over%20the%20years%20on%20all%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Wong%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessoffashion.com%2Farticles%2Fretail%2Fthe-state-of-fashion-2025-report-aritzia-interview-jennifer-wong%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Business%20of%20Fashion%20in%20January.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20say%20we%20want%20to%20be%20excellent%20at%20everything%2C%20that's%20really%20what's%20in%20our%20minds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faritzia-breakout-year-history-expansion-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753003921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68795cf83d5881a51c1d8d92%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faritzia-breakout-year-history-expansion-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%