t%3B%20he%20said.%20He%20said%20he%20made%20sure%20to%20emphasize%20his%20primary%20mission%20is%20addressing%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%2211656%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tom%20Di%20Liberto%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68781daa3d5881a51c1d7931%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%228742%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETom%20Di%20Liberto%3Cp%3EGreg%20Kahn%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20job%20search%20began%20in%20February%2C%20and%20he%20started%20his%20new%20job%20in%20early%20June.%20He%20spent%20frugally%20and%20leaned%20on%20his%20wife's%20income%20to%20support%20their%20family.%20During%20those%20months%2C%20he%20cooked%20more%20and%20cut%20back%20on%20takeout%3B%20he%20also%20prioritized%20his%20mental%20health%20with%20walks%20and%20Legos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20private%20sector%20has%20been%20an%20adjustment%2C%20he%20said.%20It's%20been%20odd%2C%20for%20example%2C%20to%20work%20with%20fewer%20people%20and%20be%20able%20to%20upgrade%20software%20quickly%20instead%20of%20over%20a%20few%20months.%20Di%20Liberto%20also%20estimated%20that%20the%20NGO%20jobs%20he%20was%20looking%20at%20paid%20between%2020%25%20and%2040%25%20less%20than%20his%20role%20at%20NOAA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20reminded%20of%20his%20past%20life%20living%20in%20DC%2C%20where%20he%20encounters%20others%20who%20were%20also%20let%20go%20from%20government%20jobs.%20Di%20Liberto's%20first%20grader%20recently%20brought%20up%20his%20father's%20job%20loss%20in%20school%2C%20where%20it%20led%20to%20a%20class-wide%20conversation%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2226384123-1cd4-40bb-b242-ed937ecb4ee4%5C%22%3EJonathan%20Kamens%2C%2055%2C%20US%20Digital%20Service%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKamens%20started%20at%20USDS%20in%202023.%20He%20was%20a%20software%20engineer%20and%20was%20detailed%20to%20a%20cybersecurity%20role%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Veterans%20Affairs.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKamens%20was%20fired%20from%20the%20US%20Digital%20Service%20%E2%80%94%20now%20the%20US%20DOGE%20Service%20%E2%80%94%20in%20February%2C%20and%20he%20landed%20a%20new%20job%20in%20March%20working%20remotely%20for%20a%20private-sector%20company%20based%20in%20Australia.%20He%20said%20that%20he's%20fortunate%20to%20be%20getting%20a%20paycheck%2C%20but%20the%20slashing%20of%20the%20federal%20workforce%20continues%20to%20weigh%20him%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20micro%2C%20I%20have%20a%20job%2C%20I'm%20getting%20paid%20to%20work%2C%20I%20can%20support%20my%20family.%20But%20in%20macro%2C%20the%20whole%20world%20is%20burning%2C%26quot%3B%20Kamens%20said.%20He%20added%20that%20it's%20difficult%20to%20live%20his%20normal%20life%20%26quot%3Band%20continue%20to%20work%20in%20a%20system%20that%20in%20many%20ways%20is%20disintegrating%20around%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20he's%20%26quot%3Bminimally%20engaged%26quot%3B%20with%20other%20colleagues%20who%20left%20the%20federal%20workforce%20because%20it%20was%20taking%20a%20toll%20on%20his%20mental%20health.%20He%20said%20public%20servants%20who%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F6-months-of-doge-federal-workers-react-layoffs-firings-trump-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estill%20employed%20with%20the%20federal%20government%20face%20challenges%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20the%20continued%20influence%20of%20DOGE.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20really%20strong%20normalcy%20bias%20happening%2C%26quot%3B%20Kamens%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20order%20for%20them%20to%20continue%20to%20function%2C%20they%20have%20to%20believe%20that%20this%20is%20just%20another%20administration%20and%20it%20will%20be%20fine%20after%20the%20midterms%20or%202028.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2257f1f132-3dae-4dab-93db-28fa1c91e064%5C%22%3ENagela%20Nukuna%2C%2030%2C%20US%20Digital%20Service%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENukuna%20started%20at%20USDS%20in%202022.%20She%20