bottle%20after%20the%20taste%20test.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rose%20wine%20bottles%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687a7553f748d8c055f5e136%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225352%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAs%20Ever%20had%20the%20highest%20alcohol%20content.%3Cp%3ENico%20Schinco%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20we%20knew%20which%20wine%20it%20was%2C%20we%20checked%20out%20the%20As%20Ever%20bottle.%20Its%2014.5%25%20alcohol%20content%20%E2%80%94%20the%20highest%20of%20the%20four%20%E2%80%94%20surprised%20us%2C%20particularly%20because%20it%20didn't%20taste%20too%20alcohol-forward.%20We%20also%20liked%20that%20the%20wine%20seemed%20versatile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAhlgrim%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20It%20is%20the%20best%20bang%20for%20your%20buck%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20the%20highest%20alcohol%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMcKenzie%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%2014.5%25%20is%20pretty%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAhlgrim%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20That%20surprises%20me%20because%20because%20of%20how%20alcohol-forward%20I%20felt%20like%20the%20Whispering%20Angel%20was.%20I%20expected%20that%20to%20be%20the%20highest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPettyjohn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20I%20like%20to%20make%20a%20ros%C3%A9%20sangria%2C%20and%20I%20think%20As%20Ever%20would%20be%20good%20with%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAhlgrim%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Ooh%2C%20with%20a%20bit%20of%20prosecco%20or%20seltzer%20in%20it%3F%20Yeah%2C%20because%20the%20flavor%20is%20so%20strong%2C%20it%20would%20lend%20itself%20well%20to%20a%20mix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPettyjohn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Yes%2C%20exactly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAhlgrim%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20It's%20not%20a%20poolside%20ros%C3%A9.%20It's%20like%20a%20charcuterie%20ros%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPettyjohn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20I%20can%20see%20Meghan%20on%20her%20patio%2C%20talking%20to%20one%20of%20her%20friends%2C%20and%20drinking%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThree%20out%20of%20the%20four%20of%20us%20could%20see%20ourselves%20buying%20As%20Ever.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224546%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tasting%20rose%20wines.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687a716d3d5881a51c1d9896%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223410%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20group%20liked%20the%20As%20Ever%20ros%C3%A9.%3Cp%3ENico%20Schinco%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAhlgrim%2C%20McKenzie%2C%20and%20I%20said%20we%20would%20buy%20As%20Ever%20down%20the%20line%2C%20though%20we%20want%20people%20to%20know%20they%20shouldn't%20expect%20a%20classic%20ros%C3%A9%20flavor.%20Rollins%20had%20reservations%2C%20especially%20because%20the%20bottles%20are%20only%20available%20in%20three%2C%20six%2C%20or%2012%20packs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERollins%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20As%20Ever%20was%20interesting%2C%20but%20I%20definitely%20wouldn't%20order%20three%20bottles%20because%20of%20the%20price%20and%20strong%20flavor.%20You%20really%20have%20to%20love%20the%20flavor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPettyjohn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20I%20would%20buy%20it!%20When%20I%20went%20to%20Sonoma%2C%20one%20winery%20had%20a%20ros%C3%A9%20you%20could%20try%2C%20and%20it%20was%20very%20similar%20to%20this.%20It%20didn't%20taste%20how%20you%20expected%20a%20ros%C3%A9%20to%20taste%2C%20but%20it%20was%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMcKenzie%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20It's%20a%20good%20wine.%20I%20would%20order%20it%20again.%20It%20was%20my%20top%20two.%20It%20tastes%20like%20a%20chardonnay%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20mind%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAhlgrim%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20Summer%20Water%20would%20be%20what%20I%20would%20drink%20on%20a%20Saturday%20during%20the%20day%20in%20the%20summer.%20Then%20I%20would%20switch%20to%20Meghan's%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPettyjohn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20I%20couldn't%20have%20said%20it%20better%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20tried%20As%20Ever's%20ros%C3%A9%20at%20home%20and%20loved%20it%20even%20more.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224996%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22As%20Ever%20rose%20wine%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687a6d8085e81483682e4682%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%226245%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAs%20Ever%20ros%C3%A9.%3Cp%3ENico%20Schinco%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20after%20the%20official%20taste%20test%2C%20I%20revisited%20As%20Ever%20ros%C3%A9%2C%20pouring%20a%20glass%20for%20myself%20and%20my%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20gave%20it%20a%20sniff%2C%20inhaling%20that%20full-bodied%2C%20almost%20orange%20wine-like%20scent%20that%20surprised%20me%20during%20the%20test.%20It%20was%20inviting%20and%20bright%2C%20and%20as%20I%20took%20a%20sip%2C%20I%20was%20delighted%20that%20As%20Ever%20tasted%20even%20more%20refreshing%20and%20crisp%20than%20I%20remembered.%20My%20husband%20was%20a%20fan%2C%20too%2C%20and%20I%20had%20to%20remind%20myself%20not%20to%20drink%20it%20too%20quickly%20over%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeghan's%20ros%C3%A9%20is%20a%20hit%20in%20my%20book%2C%20and%20I'm%20intrigued%20to%20see%20how%20her%20foray%20into%20the%20wine%20industry%20continues.%20Cheers!%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeghan-markle-as-ever-rose-wine-review-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753002902000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687ab4c0f748d8c055f5ea11%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeghan-markle-as-ever-rose-wine-review-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meghan%20Markle's%20As%20Ever%20brand%20launched%20its%20first%20wine%2C%20a%20ros%C3%A9%20from%20Napa%20Valley.%20We%20compared%20it%20to%20other%20popular%20ros%C