C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20job%2C%20Indeed%20found.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECareer%20coaches%20told%20BI%20that%20your%20speed%20can%20signal%20your%20interest%20in%20a%20role.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-job-search-tool-apply-dream-role-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elooking%20for%20a%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20speed%20is%20your%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%2C%20like%20in%20business%20itself%2C%20there%20is%20often%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthis-is-the-nightmare-scenario-for-grubhub-experts-say-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efirst-mover%20advantage%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20job%20seekers%20who%20respond%20quickly%20to%20open%20roles%20and%20overtures%20from%20employers%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20job%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApplying%20to%20a%20role%20within%20the%20first%2010%20minutes%20of%20getting%20a%20relevant%20job%20alert%20can%20boost%20your%20chance%20of%20hearing%20back%20by%20as%20much%20as%20four%20times%2C%20LinkedIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopportunity.linkedin.com%2Fjobs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efound%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaste%20can%20also%20pay%20off%20throughout%20the%20process%2C%20especially%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewhen%20it%20comes%20to%20responding%20to%20those%20doing%20the%20hiring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20job%20seekers%20who%20reply%20to%20a%20prospective%20employer's%20message%20within%2024%20hours%20are%204.1%20times%20as%20likely%20to%20get%20hired%20and%206.7%20times%20as%20likely%20to%20get%20an%20interview%2C%20according%20to%20data%20Indeed%20shared%20with%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSpeed%20is%20not%20just%20an%20edge%2C%20it's%20a%20signal%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Patrice%20Lindo%2C%20CEO%20of%20Career%20Nomad%2C%20a%20platform%20that%20helps%20professionals%20navigate%20career%20changes.%20%26quot%3BIt%20says%2C%20'I'm%20ready.%20I'm%20visible.%20I'm%20serious.%20I'm%20a%20decision-maker.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20recommends%20that%20clients%20apply%20for%20jobs%20within%20the%20first%20four%20to%20eight%20hours%20of%20seeing%20a%20posting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20far%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20seen%20and%20even%20considered%2C%26quot%3B%20Lindo%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220c8c12a7-d7b2-4a67-8706-acced17ee6e8%5C%22%3EA%20sign%20of%20intent%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20difference%20that%20speed%20can%20make%20matters%20because%2C%20for%20many%20desk%20workers%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbi-today-everyone-rethinking-job-market-networking-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epace%20of%20hiring%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20gone%20from%20blazing%20fast%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20to%20sluggish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20overall%20job%20market%20remains%20strong%2C%20yet%20some%20companies%20are%20taking%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchanging-jobs-risky-move-now-recession-economic-uncertainty-tariffs-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etime%20to%20hire%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20they%20try%20to%20gain%20insights%20into%20factors%20such%20as%20how%20tariff%20vacillations%20could%20affect%20the%20economy%20and%20how%20quickly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-replace-jobs-or-increase-worker-productivity-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20take%20on%20certain%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%2C%20in%20this%20market%2C%20moving%20quickly%20isn't%20a%20sign%20of%20desperation%2C%20but%20rather%20of%20intent%2C%20Lindo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20reason%20to%20be%20speedy%20is%20that%20once%20an%20employer%20has%20a%20sufficient%20number%20of%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%2C%20they're%20likely%20to%20stop%20looking%20at%20whatever%20else%20trickles%20in%2C%20Susan%20Peppercorn%2C%20an%20executive%20and%20career%20coach%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20advises%20clients%20that%2C%20most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20it's%20not%20worth%20it%20to%20apply%20for%20a%20role%20when%20the%20number%20of%20applicants%20reaches%20100.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeppercorn%2C%20like%20Lindo%2C%20said%20that%20moving%20fast%20can%20send%20a%20positive%20signal%20when%20communicating%20with%20a%20would-be%20employer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BResponding%20within%2024%20hours%20anybody%20can%20do%2C%20but%20responding%20within%20the%20first%20hour%20shows%20that%20you're%20really%2C%20really%20interested%2C%26quot%3B%20Peppercorn%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f11b4a97-268d-4a10-a5e8-dd731a5605d4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoing%20your%20homework%20quickly%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMoving%20fast%20doesn't%20give%20you%20a%20license%20to%20be%20sloppy%2C%20of%20course.%20It's%20still%20better%20to%20tailor%20your%20applications%20to%20each%20job%20and%20to%20include%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-write-the-perfect-cover-letter-2014-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecover%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%2C%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20mentions%20the%20employer's%20name%20and%20the%20role%20you're%20going%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECustomizing%20an%20application%20while%20also%20moving%20fast%20can%20be%20challenging%2C%20but%20it's%20doable%20if%20you're%20prepared.%20Lindo%20likened%20it%20to%20how%20a%20pregnant%20woman%20might%20prepare%20a%20bag%20packed%20with%20essentials%20for%20the%20hospital.%20Translation%3A%20Have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-search-networking-resume-early-career-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20strong%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%3C%2Fa%3E%20ready%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20way%2C%20it%20only%20needs%20small%20adjustments%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20opportunity%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeppercorn%20recommends%20limiting%20what%20you%20tweak%20to%20create%20a%20solid%20but%20speedy%20application.%20She%20said%20job%20applicants%20should%20focus%20on%20the%20top%20summary%20section%20of%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20and%2C%20where%20possible%2C%20leave%20the%20other%20sections%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20edits%20you%20make%20to%20the%20top%20should%20incorporate%20some%20of%20the%20key%20words%20contained%20in%20the%20job%20posting%2C%20Peppercorn%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20include%20a%20cover%20letter%2C%20she%20said%2C%20the%20software%20that%20many%20employers%20use%20to%20collate%20applications%20often%20strips%20off%20that%20layer%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20itself.%20So%2C%20Peppercorn%20said%2C%20a%20perfunctory%20cover%20letter%20with%20some%20modest%20customization%20might%20often%20suffice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20any%20case%2C%20don't%20take%20too%20long.%20Otherwise%2C%20you%20risk%20missing%20out%20because%20some%20employers%20close%20openings%20within%20five%20to%2010%20days%2C%20Lindo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20an%20employer%20doesn't%20take%20down%20a%20listing%2C%20if%20you're%20still%20perfecting%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20on%20day%20eight%2C%20%26quot%3Byou've%20already%20missed%20the%20window%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELindo%20added%20that%20some%20employers%20are%20likely%20to%20think%20that%20applicants%20who%20move%20quickly%20would%20also%20apply%20that%20approach%20to%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20indicator%20of%20how%20you%20will%20operate%20if%20you%20were%20to%20be%20chosen%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20your%20job%20search%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Atparadis%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Etparadis%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider