%20the%20OpenAI%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20my%20job%20to%20explain%20to%20the%20company%20our%20path%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20Windsurf's%20new%20CEO%2C%20Jeff%20Wang%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%20Wang%20was%20formerly%20the%20company's%20head%20of%20business.%20He%20had%20planned%20to%20discuss%20the%20options%20%E2%80%94%20fundraising%20from%20VCs%2C%20selling%20the%20company%20to%20someone%20else%2C%20distributing%20remaining%20cash%2C%20or%20just%20keeping%20it%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20mood%20was%20very%20bleak%2C%26quot%3B%20Wang%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BSome%20people%20were%20upset%20about%20financial%20outcomes%20or%20colleagues%20leaving%2C%20while%20others%20were%20worried%20about%20the%20future.%20A%20few%20were%20in%20tears.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20that%20day%2C%20a%20ray%20of%20light%20emerged.%20Wang%20said%20Cognition%20cofounder%20Scott%20Wu%2C%20and%20its%20president%2C%20Russell%20Kaplan%2C%20reached%20out.%20They%20wanted%20what%20was%20left%20of%20Windsurf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECognition%20makes%20the%20AI%20coding%20agent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcognition-labs-devin-ai-software-engineer-humans-lose-jobs-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDevin%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20it%20calls%20%26quot%3Bthe%20first%20AI%20software%20engineer.%26quot%3B%20It%20is%20valued%20at%20%244%20billion%2C%20coming%20off%20a%20%24120%20million%20funding%20round%20in%20March%2C%20according%20to%20PitchBook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWang%20saw%20the%20melding%20of%20the%20company's%20products%20as%20a%20potential%20win-win.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDevin%20would%20benefit%20from%20a%20foreground%20synchronous%20agent%2C%20while%20we%20needed%20a%20remote%20asynchronous%20agent%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20Added%20to%20that%2C%20he%20was%20excited%20about%20both%20companies%20sharing%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dealmaking%20kicked%20off%20immediately.%20They%20brought%20in%20lawyers%20and%20s