0And%20the%20success%20story%20of%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20electrification%20holds%20a%20mirror%20up%20to%20this.%20In%202019%2C%20when%20the%20district%20tasted%20a%2024%2F7%20power%20supply%20%E2%80%94%20through%20the%20collaborative%20efforts%20of%20Gram%20Oorja%20and%20NGO%20PRADAN%20%E2%80%94%20it%20did%20more%20than%20enable.%20It%20empowered.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20the%20villagers%20take%20charge%20of%20the%20grid%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20access%20to%20an%20unbroken%20flow%20of%20electricity%20meant%20the%20women%20could%20breeze%20through%20their%20chores.%20No%20longer%20relegated%20to%20the%20home%2C%20they%20optimised%20the%20extra%20time%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20Village%20Energy%20Committee%20(VEC)%2C%20where%20they%20got%20to%20be%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20decisions%20that%20would%20become%20the%20bedrock%20for%20village%20development%20%E2%80%94%20from%20calling%20the%20shots%20on%20energy%20tariffs%20to%20assigning%20the%20operational%20logistics%20to%20an%20elected%20local%20operator.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fhome-garden-1-1752771702.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20women%20of%20Jharkhand%20have%20become%20an%20active%20part%20in%20the%20decision-making%20process%20regarding%20the%20solar%20microgrids%20%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fhome-garden-1-1752771702.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fhome-garden-1-1752771702-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fhome-garden-1-1752771702-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fhome-garden-1-1752771702-