ant%20them%20to%20also%20benefit%20from%20solar.%20We%20are%20saving%20for%20our%20future.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBacked%20by%20Gram%20Oorja%2C%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Gumla%20are%20turning%20into%20custodians%20of%20their%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20success%20of%20the%20model%2C%20Sameer%2C%20one%20of%20the%20founders%20of%20Gram%20Oorja%2C%20says%20it%E2%80%99s%20hinged%20on%20two%20key%20players%20%E2%80%94%20CSR%20grants%20(which%20help%20with%20capital%20costs)%20and%20tariffs%2C%20which%20cover%20the%20maintenance%20costs.%20The%20latter%20is%20as%20crucial%20as%20the%20former%20because%20they%20allow%20for%20a%20judicious%20use%20of%20the%20resources.%20This%20is%20important%2C%20he%20explains%2C%20as%20when%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F268152%2Fmaharashtra-village-manyachiwadi-solar-gram-electricity-sustainable-women-success%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elocals%20witness%20continuous%20power%20supply%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20tendency%20to%20view%20it%20as%20a%20rare%20indulgence.%20Tariffs%20ensure%20prudent%20use.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaking%20them%20a%20part%20of%20the%20process%20ensures%20that%20the%20model%20goes%20beyond%20a%20fleeting%20inclusion%20and%20instead%20sustains%20itself%20in%20the%20long%20run.%20Over%20the%20life%20cycle%20of%20the%20project%2C%20the%20village%20bears%20around%2060%20percent%20of%20the%20overall%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Gumla%2C%20a%20constant%20power%20supply%20guarantees%20more%20than%20just%20peace%20of%20mind.%20It%20also%20lends%20them%20a%20quiet%20confidence%20to%20start%20dabbling%20in%20economics%20beyond%20what%20they%E2%80%99re%20comfortable%20with%20on%20home%20turf.%20Sameer%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThrough%20solar%2C%20the%20people%20of%20the%20village%20can%20grow%20an%20extra%20crop%2C%20engage%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F467095%2Fsolar-dryer-based-business%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eagricultural%20processing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20adopt%20dehusking%20machines.%20These%20things%20add%20to%20their%20income%3B%20they%20make%20the%20system%20more%20viable.%20So%20you%20see%2C%20with%20a%20subsidy%2C%20the%20project%20would%20run%20for%20around%20four%20years.%20But%20the%20idea%20is%20to%20make%20it%20run%20forever.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20energy%20becomes%20an%20enabler%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHow%20can%20energy%20access%20transform%20the%20villages%20of%20India%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20Sameer%20and%20Anshuman%20bent%20their%20heads%20over%20the%20question.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20contextualise%20their%20concerns%2C%20we%20revisit%20a%202015%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%2C%20which%20underscored%20that%20even%20though%20India%20was%20officially%20declared%20100%20percent%20electrified%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20just%2010%20percent%20of%20homes%20in%20a%20village%20had%20to%20have%20electricity%20to%20meet%20the%20criteria%20%E2%80%94%2017%20percent%20of%20homes%20were%20still%20without%20power.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20bothered%20them.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20ideating%20on%20the%20best%20way%20to%20create%20impact%20in%20the%20villages%2C%20we%20struck%20upon%20the%20idea%20of%20energy%20access.%20We%E2%80%99re%20talking%20about%20a%20time%20when%20fossil%20fuel%20prices%20were%20steadily%20rising.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20you%20had%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F418409%2Findia-solar-power-electricity-bill-savings%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20renewable%20energy%20becoming%20more%20accessible%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20idea%20was%20to%20take%20both%