hop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T171459.165_11zon-1752666310-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T171459.165_11zon-1752666310-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T171459.165_11zon-1752666310-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T171459.165_11zon-1752666310-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-471038%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESwuyievezo%20Dzudo%20has%20built%20a%20low-cost%20solar%20dryer%2C%20an%20electricity-free%20device%20that%E2%80%99s%20helping%20farmers%20preserve%20their%20produce%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20Porba%2C%20he%20began%20spending%20time%20with%20farmers%2C%20listening%20to%20their%20daily%20struggles.%20And%20somewhere%20in%20those%20conversations%2C%20he%20asked%20what%20they%20did%20with%20the%20leftover%20harvest.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20told%20me%20they%20had%20no%20reliable%20electricity%2C%20making%20it%20almost%20impossible%20to%20preserve%20their%20surplus%20crops%20properly.%20This%20led%20to%20huge%20losses%2C%20as%20the%20excess%20would%20simply%20rot%20or%20be%20turned%20into%20compost.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20infrastructure%20lagging%20far%20behind%2C%20many%20hilly%20parts%20of%20Nagaland%20still%20face%20severe%20power%20shortages%20%E2%80%94%20and%20when%20electricity%20is%20available%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20often%20too%20erratic%20to%20rely%20on.%20As%20Swuyievezo%20listened%20to%20the%20farmers%2C%20this%20recurring%20challenge%20kept%20surfacing.%20Over%20time%2C%20it%20became%20clear%20to%20him%20that%20any%20real%20solution%20would%20need%20to%20work%20without%20relying%20on%20power%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20he%20began%20exploring%20the%20idea%20of%20building%20a%20solar%20dryer%20%E2%80%94%20something%20simple%2C%20affordable%2C%20and%20effective%20that%20could%20help%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F388195%2Fkanpur-farmer-shivraj-nishad-solar-dryer-dehydrated-flower-business-blue-veda%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreserve%20fresh%20produce%20without%20electricity%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20collaborating%20with%20Kirat%20Biotech%20Private%20Limited%20in%20Guwahati%20and%20took%20guidance%20from%20ICAR%E2%80%99s%20Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendra%20(KVK)%20in%20Phek.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20partnerships%20allowed%20me%20to%20understand%20the%20exact%20problems%20farmers%20face%20and%20helped%20shape%20the%20design%20of%20the%20dryer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBeer%20cans%2C%20bamboo%20%26amp%3B%20a%20bit%20of%20sunlight%20changed%20the%20game%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20its%20simplest%2C%20solar%20drying%20is%20just%20using%20sunlight%20to%20remove%20moisture%20from%20crops%20%E2%80%94%20a%20way%20to%20keep%20fruits%2C%20vegetables%2C%20and%20medicinal%20plants%20from%20going%20bad.%20Farmers%20have%20done%20it%20for%20generations%2C%20but%20the%20traditional%20method%20has%20its%20limits.%20Left%20out%20in%20the%20open%2C%20the%20produce%20gets%20hit%20by%20dust%2C%20insects%2C%20sudden%20rain%2C%20and%20harsh%20sunlight%20that%20can%20spoil%20both%20taste%20and%20quality.%20Industrial%20dryers%20solve%20these%20problems%20but%20come%20with%20high%20costs%20and%20require%20a%20steady%20electricity%20supply%20%E2%80%94%20something%20most%20rural%20farmers%20don%E2%80%99t%20have.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%2