0%9CWe%20used%20bamboo%20and%20wood%20for%20the%20main%20structure%20because%20these%20are%20abundant%20in%20our%20village%20and%20inexpensive%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20Bamboo%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20is%20lightweight%2C%20strong%2C%20and%20sustainable%2C%20making%20it%20ideal%20for%20rural%20construction.%20To%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F448564%2Fcommunities-come-together-to-tackle-heat%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabsorb%20heat%20efficiently%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20dryer%20incorporates%20an%20ingenious%20solar%20accumulator%20made%20from%20empty%20aluminium%20beer%20cans.%20These%20cans%20store%20the%20sun%E2%80%99s%20heat%2C%20creating%20a%20consistent%20warming%20effect%20inside%20the%20drying%20chamber.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20retain%20heat%20and%20protect%20the%20produce%20from%20harsh%20direct%20sunlight%2C%20Swuyievezo%20initially%20used%20acrylic%20sheets%2C%20but%20later%20switched%20to%20glass%20sheets%2C%20which%20are%20more%20durable%20and%20better%20for%20insulation.%20The%20drying%20chamber%20is%20lined%20with%20UV-protective%20sheets%20that%20filter%20out%20harmful%20rays%2C%20shielding%20the%20produce%20from%20damage%20and%20keeping%20insects%20and%20pests%20at%20bay.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20exhaust%20fan%2C%20powered%20by%20a%20small%20solar%20panel%2C%20ensures%20continuous%20airflow%20and%20removes%20excess%20moisture%20%E2%80%94%20creating%20an%20optimal%20drying%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20was%20balancing%20heat%20retention%20with%20proper%20airflow%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20innovator%20notes.%20%E2%80%9CToo%20much%20humidity%20would%20cause%20mould%2C%20but%20too%20little%20airflow%20would%20slow%20the%20drying%20process.%20We%20experimented%20with%20fan%20placement%2C%20materials%2C%20and%20layouts%20until%20we%20found%20the%20right%20balance.%E2%